snippet.title: Tanks vs Tanks - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Tanks vs Tanks is a tank battle simulator game where you try to destroy as many enemy tanks as possible. You have unlimited but time-based bullets. Pay attention to your health and don't forget to collect extra health.

Developed and published by Warlock Arts
Also released on PlayStation 5
